snippet.title: House of Lost Souls - STEAM ANNOUNCEMENT
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2636000

Long-standing pain forced Jack to return to the old family home in search of answers. Find out the terrible truth that this house kept, and how it relates to what happened to his parents in the distant past.
